attributes.comment:
I am writing to you in regards to raising the fee for the I-600A and the
fingerprinting fee. I was upset to hear this. My husband and I are currently
awaiting a referral from China. Our paperwork will expire and I was
disheartened to hear that we would have to pay even more money. I really feel
that it would be nice if the fee was not raised for those who are already in the
process and just have to renew there paperwork. Even better yet, it would be
nice if there was a re-application/renewal fee that was different than the
initial application fee.

I appreciate you taking the time to listen.

Thank you much!
attributes.title: Comment Submitted By Melissa Jenkins
